@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Login (get JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user234@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "user234",
    "email": "user234@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Get all users (requires JWT — paste token below)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer <paste_token_here>

### Create user directly (bypasses hashing — for DB debugging only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "user234",
    "email": "user234@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}
